Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:46.77,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}恋への階段
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:51.88,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}私は登ろうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.63,OPjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}決めて！
